01:53:46.010 --> 01:53:50.050
INSURRECTION À UDON

01:53:47.560 --> 01:53:49.870
Udon se rebelle.

01:53:50.660 --> 01:53:52.000
C’est formidable,

01:53:52.390 --> 01:53:54.250
petit gars de paille !

01:54:04.200 --> 01:54:07.570
Tu as vraiment dégoté
un allié de taille,

01:54:08.340 --> 01:54:09.590
mon petit Kinémon !